{"tid":2169294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做到呢樣野，Apple Store 膠層一定要回應！","createTime":"2020-08-22T11:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T02:19:59.000Z","uid":370528,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"33e7c12cc450deadb3ef295588d91119477510c1","tid":2169294,"uid":370528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">蘋果版圍魏救趙</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地知唔知Apple Store個核彈喺邊度呀？<br />\n係客戶意見呀！係<span class=\"red\">survey</span>呀！<br />\n你send幾多個email俾gay cook都會落咗上海支那手上！<br />\n而survey係全球都會睇到！<br />\n到時香港班膠層自然要解話！要照肺！自然唔會高調政治審查<br />\n<br />\n前線藍精靈基本上全部黃，但無得發聲，比完意見只係會比漠視！（更多資料可以去睇下Facebook page &rdquo;蘋果的二三事2.0 &ldquo;）<br />\n<span class=\"red\">膠層最近不停高調講<span class=\"large\">平權、共融</span>，話最尊重人權乜乜乜，又拎BLM事件出黎打飛機！香港既共融只係包容唔同性格咋！呢一年既事絕口不提！</span><br />\n<br />\n好喇！講左咁多野<br />\n咁點先有得填survey? <br />\n<br />\n方法係你要行入去買野，係呀我知好on9<br />\n可以買iTunes gift card都得，或者買$8 iTunes Pass（虛擬），之後課金用返！<br />\n記得叫班藍精靈send 收據去email<br />\n最好印埋紙收據對下個email有無打錯！<br />\n點解？你懂的<br />\n去Genius Bar維修都得！但出問卷係隨機！<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><br />\n收據會連埋survey五分鐘後一齊send俾你 !<br />\n除左個同事評分比5分，其餘全部俾1分，係呀，係1分！</span><br />\n之後就可以寫底你想留嘅意見！建議最好填英文！無諗法可以讚下幫你既藍精靈，<span class=\"large\">但係一定要寫間鋪，直接d就話見到藍口罩覺得唔舒服！或者寫點解蘋果講平權但無為香港發聲！</span><br />\n最後可以㨂經理需唔需要打電話比你，呢個㨂唔㨂都得！<br />\n但最重要係比1分！<br />\n<br />\n基本上香港每一間鋪一星期收到30-50份問卷，每星期每間鋪都有10個「1分」，膠層已經要跪！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">Survey每次買野都可以填！<br />\n兄弟爬山！越多人做越好！<br />\n靠各路手足迫到港共膠層跪低！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nApple 高層說謊成性，當香港人係傻嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2166881\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2166881</a><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒真係寫咗公開信俾Tim Cook！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2167867\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2167867</a>"},{"pid":"785f8071799d865b0186448d0a23b24b21ddb03f","tid":2169294,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:15:07.000Z","msg":"送錢比cook<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f11d5ac4458ebf422f79f19ffc8f796c38c8a8","tid":2169294,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d22dc84d8e285ecd2af1521e4ad485a57758e8f","tid":2169294,"uid":370528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"785f8071799d865b0186448d0a23b24b21ddb03f","tid":2169294,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:15:07.000Z","msg":"送錢比cook<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:59:11.000Z","msg":"唔一定買貴野，iTunes pass 入$1都得"},{"pid":"5d07f989260e59cf497427e84d6b57a48efcb5a3","tid":2169294,"uid":110459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f0a063fde589f41c83e32fa7dc6e61cd46f3affa","tid":2169294,"uid":178066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:11:48.000Z","msg":"仲要比錢佢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11c1bff510518f3adc217b8064d23d77536dba1","tid":2169294,"uid":370528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T02:52:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c45d5aa8723f75708b1a4fb1e9166be0863002e4","tid":2169294,"uid":107727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有朋友係入面做前線員工，<br />\n班香港膠層離地到同班地方官一樣，<br />\n對外在就包裝到好共融，事實上仲衰過港資公司 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6ce3d194be4fef66d7ea481ed0a0217934a9ca","tid":2169294,"uid":31166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"即係填問卷<br />\n近年好似好多公司，服務性行業<br />\n如果啲客人唔填最高分<br />\n就好似係冇用，呢啲系統真係累死人<br />\n咁如果我10分覺得8分已經好高分呢<br />\n<br />\n但原來個同事攞到8分，公司係覺得佢成績唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71820ea16